  "subject": "Fix trace context propagation for AAI requests",
  "commit_message": "Fix trace context propagation for AAI requests\n\n- ensure trace context propagation by dependency injecting\n  an executor instead of spawning new threads (via new Thread())\n  for each request towards AAI\n- a thread pool also saves the overhead of spawning new threads\n  each time\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4366\nChange-Id: Iec32b8a9346ba8f40b951b38441f6ee67c17fa50\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
